features: STRONG AND DURABLE: This robust bed base is fully constructed of metal frame for large load-bearing capacity. Reliable frame features 12 metal slats between two sides which provides you with strong support for a relaxing sleep. The powder-coated surface features medium rust and scratch resistance for long term use. Besides, not shaky after proper assembly.

CLASSIC AND ROMANTIC: This farmhouse styled bed features curved lines and thick tube frames, bringing a romantic and warm feeling to your space. The beautiful silhouette subtly balances the coolness of metal that is easily blended with modern, traditional, farmhouse and rustic home decors.

HIGH HEADBOARD DESIGN: Compared with other metal beds, this classic bed frame has a higher headboard for better protecting your head and providing you a comfortable sitting place. You can prop soft pillows behind your back, and read books or watch TV lazily.

VERSATILE: We care about the practical use of every piece we made, this platform bed has 32cm/12.5” of clearance underneath the bed for a clean and tidy space. Ideal for guest rooms, bedrooms, dormitories, apartments and temporary stay.

SAFE: Carefully designed, this mattress foundation is built of round corners, smooth finish and protective footpads, which is safer for our customers to use. Moreover, the high foot board keeps bedding from falling onto the floor while you sleep.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 10, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars A solid sturdy bargain!
reviews.reviewText: I bought this for a guest room. I was initially somewhat skeptical based on the price (5 stars for affordability), but I figured I'd take a risk because it was, after all, for a guest room. I was pleasantly surprised. It is VERY sturdy. Let's walk through unboxing, assembly, and my finished assessment.Unboxing: everything came well packaged, yet with minimal styrofoam waste. No damaged pieces. Impressed so far!Assembly: Took me about 2 hours using the included tools and watching a Hallmark movie. Might have gone a little faster had I used power tools. Instructions were easy to read and clear. Parts were clearly labeled.The screws/bolts/nuts were in labeled blisterpacks. A few extras were included just in case, although I didnt need them. Holes were drilled out correctly. I had no trouble putting pieces together. It went together smoothly. I did a final tightening of everything and snugged it all up.Stability/Sturdiness: Admittedly, I was initially a bit skeptical. The frame gets progressively more sturdy as it comes together, I promise. I was also concerned the round mattress rails seemed narrow, however, my concerns were unfounded. I put a 12 inch memory foam mattress (also purchased here on Amazon) right on top of the frame. It fit snugly between the head and foot rails, so it doesn't shift around (win!). I can't feel the rails through the mattress; no lumps or hard spots (win!). There are no squeaks or wobble in the frame. It is STURDY (double win!)Final assessment: I have no complaints with this product. It was extremely affordable. It's sturdy. It's attractive. Very pleased with this purchase! I know I mentioned using this in a guest room, but I would have no reservations purchasing another for everyday use. Great value for your money!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 15, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars great bed frame
reviews.reviewText: Great frame at a very reasonable price. I am a petite older female and had no problem unpacking and assembling by myself. I did use my own tools which I preferred to the ones provided. (Allen wrench and a crescent) Instructions were straightforward and easy to follow. I had watched the video before purchasing but didn't need to view during assembly. I bought the bronze and it looks much like the picture. This bed looks beautiful. I think this style is very versatile and would work well with farmhouse, boho, shabby chic, rustic, western, or eclectic decor. Legends never die. Happy customer-me .

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 18, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Easy to put together
reviews.reviewText: Bought this bed for Christmas. My daughter actually put it together by herself. No extra tools required. It took her about an hour. The bed is sturdy. Does not make noise when you move around. Great bed for the price. Very stylish.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 15, 2024
reviews.reviewText: This bed is a great value. Looks really nice and is sturdy- comes in MANY parts and need organization and patience to put together. It is not hard, just lots of bolts that need to be tightened. My screw package was ripped open when it arrived so it was a pain to figure out which ones were which, and a few were missing. But I love the bed and would order again.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 23, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Beautiful bed frame
reviews.reviewText: I purchased the gold frame and it's a beautiful color! It is perfect and sturdy enough for my young teen. There were alot of pieces to put together but wasn't hard at all to assemble. One of the mattress slats did arrive cracked but I reached out to the company and they sent me another one quickly. Will definitely purchase again in the future when I upgrade my other daughter's bed.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 1, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars sturdy & easy to assemble
reviews.reviewText: I was quite impressed with this bedframe. Well-made and attractive. It is shipped in a box containing a huge number of parts but if you take your time, separate all the components, and work through the detailed pictorial instructions, you can get it assembled quickly. They have included a spare of every bolt & washer, just in case, and also the required assembly wrench. Good product!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 2, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Would definitely buy again!
reviews.reviewText: Beautiful bedframe. We are the type to not really use headboards/footboard, we just get a frame with a base. Nothing fancy. However, we treated ourself to a California king mattress and this frame was too good of a deal to pass up. Very cute. Took about 2 hours for me to put together. Relatively simple, except when you have to use the Alan to turn the screw and the other tool just to hold the nut in place. Maybe there is a better way, but it was the quickest way for me to tighten the screw. This is only my second time putting together furniture, first time bedframe, and I managed pretty well. The metal seems great quality, as well. As sturdy as if it was one piece. Lots of space underneath too. Remember that it is just coated antique gold so be gentle when assembling.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 24, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Beautiful and Easy assembly
reviews.reviewText: I bought this for my 16-year-old daughter because her old wood bedframe broke. She picked this out and I am very grateful that she picked out a very good product. The price is good and affordable. She actually put the product together herself and did a great job. She said that the instructions were very easy and it came with everything she needed. Thank you for providing, a reliable and good quality product.

My last bed that I had for 10 years recently broke, and I was looking for something that was more sturdier as my previous bed was made of wood, then I came up on this beautiful farm style metal frame and fell in love. You can put it together alone or with someone else but someone else obviously obviously makes it a lot easier and quicker. It’s extremely sturdy and I love the fact that the metal bar slats are very close together so it doesn’t make my memory foam mattress sag on the bottom in between the slats. The end result looks beautiful, and I love the fact that, even though it’s a queen size it takes up so much less space in my room than my previous bed! Definitely recommend! Took me about 45 minutes to put together and everything is neatly packed with very clear detailed instructions
